snippet.title: Alex Zane Tells Awkward Stories From Interviewing Joaquin Phoenix & Amber Heard 😳 | The Movie Dweeb
snippet.description:
Days after hosting the UK's coverage of The Academy Awards, Alex Zane spoke about accidentally calling Amber Heard by the wrong name, and having a tense exchange with Joker's Joaquin Phoenix.

It's not all awkward, though - Alex also spoke about receiving a personalised cake from Tom Cruise every Christmas.

He also spoke about this year's Oscars ceremony; reviewing Daniel Kaluuya's speech, Frances McDormand howling, and Glenn Close's twerking, and even picked West Side Story and King Richard as contenders for next year's award season.
